				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I've heard alot about these, in theory I've heard they do turn into a hammer, and the hammer has a similar effect, overall its awesome because you get 2 items for the price of one.  Not only that, for an int caster this is heavan, more health, +20 int on gloves?  thats unparalleled.  I've yet to hear of anyone having the guts to right click on them and test the effect, but I predict that they are expendable because otherwise you could create a hundred hammers without losing the gloves.  I think similarly, the hammer would transmute back into gloves with one charge of transmute hammer.  Between the saves, int and sta, not to mention that added effect AND an AC of 16?!? that would make most tanks drool.  If you get these, consider yourself LUCKY.
